* Usage

  The simplest usage is just to put the Plugin into the reporting area
  and use it default values.

+---
<project>
  ...
  <reporting>
    <plugin>
      <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
      <artifactId>${project.artifactId}</artifactId>
      <version>${project.version}</version>
    </plugin>
  </reporting>
  ...
<project>
+---


+---
<project>
  ...
  <reporting>
    <plugin>
      <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
      <artifactId>${project.artifactId}</artifactId>
      <version>${project.version}</version>
      <configuration>
        <haveDot>false</haveDot>
        <quiet>false</quiet>
        <projectName>This is a Test Project (basicReportTest)</projectName>
      </configuration>
    </plugin>
  </reporting>
  ...
